- Hey, sweetheart.

35:26.024 --> 35:29.793
- Isn't this so fun, a
night out altogether?

35:29.828 --> 35:30.827
- What do you think
of this place?

35:30.863 --> 35:32.462
- It's very loud.

35:33.465 --> 35:34.731
- You know, Memphis is
home of the Blues, Jazz--

35:34.766 --> 35:36.666
- How long does this
go on, you know?

35:36.702 --> 35:37.534
- This song?

35:37.569 --> 35:38.668
- The evening.

35:38.704 --> 35:41.071
(cheering)

35:42.341 --> 35:47.110
- Lafayette's you've been
wonderful, thank y'all so much.

35:47.146 --> 35:50.080
- All right now, we got
some special performers

35:50.115 --> 35:51.381
coming to the stage.

35:51.416 --> 35:54.718
So please, give a
warm round of applause

35:54.753 --> 35:57.487
to Laurel Couper
and Clay Sheppard.

35:57.523 --> 35:58.255
- Us?

35:58.290 --> 36:00.590
(cheering)

36:00.626 --> 36:01.858
- You know anything about this?

36:01.894 --> 36:03.727
- No, daddy, I swear.

36:04.730 --> 36:06.163
- Oh Laurel, y'all
get on up there.

36:06.198 --> 36:07.931
- What I tell you, the
best act in Memphis,

36:07.966 --> 36:10.367
and perfect to perform
at your wedding.

36:10.402 --> 36:11.801
- Are you sure you
want to do this?

36:11.837 --> 36:14.337
- Not much of a choice now.

36:14.373 --> 36:16.339
Sal, you know I hate
being put on the spot.

36:16.375 --> 36:18.108
- Get used to it, you're
gonna be front and center

36:18.143 --> 36:19.409
for them soon anyway.

36:19.444 --> 36:22.712
(crowd applauding)

36:24.816 --> 36:26.049
- Let's hear some music!

36:26.084 --> 36:28.518
(cheering)

36:28.554 --> 36:30.554
- Well fine, y'all
put us on the spot

36:30.589 --> 36:31.655
and we're up here now.

36:31.690 --> 36:32.789
What do y'all wanna hear?

36:32.824 --> 36:34.891
- How about some Elvis?

36:36.962 --> 36:38.328
- All right.

